query:
-- Comparar totais
SELECT 'Leads' as tipo, COUNT(*) as total FROM quiz_responses WHERE leadEmail IS NOT NULL
UNION ALL
SELECT 'Personais' as tipo, COUNT(*) as total FROM personals
UNION ALL
SELECT 'Leads que viraram Personal' as tipo, COUNT(*) as total 
FROM quiz_responses qr
JOIN users u ON LOWER(qr.leadEmail) = LOWER(u.email)
JOIN personals p ON u.id = p.userId;
